The paper discusses the use of biometric features for authentication and authorization of mobile IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also mentions the use of machine learning and data mining methods, which could be classified under machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses threat models and countermeasures, which could be classified under security and privacy (cs.SI).
